    <div class="container1">
        <div class="h3 border-bottom border-secondary" id="h1">회원가입</div>
        <div class="form-floating" id="log">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="hosID" placeholder="ID">
            <label for="floatingInput">아이디를 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        
        <div class="form-floating" id="log2">
            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Password">
            <label for="floatingPassword">비밀번호를 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="container2">
            <div class="form-floating" id="pw">
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password2" placeholder="Password check">
                <label for="floatingPassword">비밀번호를 다시 입력하세요.</label>
            </div>
            <div class="check">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check" onclick="check()" id="che"></i>
            </div>    
        </div>
        <div class="line" style="color:gray; margin-top: 20px;">-------------- 병원 정보 입력란 --------------</div>

        <div class="form-floating" id="log2">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="hosName" placeholder="name">
            <label for="floatingInput">병원 이름을 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="category" style="display: flex; text-align: center; margin-top: 7px; margin-bottom: 7px;">
            <div class="content1" style="  padding: 10px; padding-right: 26px; padding-left: 25px;
            margin-right: 10px; border: 1px gainsboro solid; border-radius: 5px;">
                Category<br>
                선택
            </div>
            <div class="content2" style="border: 1px gainsboro solid; border-radius: 5px;padding: 10px;">
                <div class="cate1" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="jh"> 정형외과 </label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="sk"> 신경외과 </label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="eye"> 안과</label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="no"> 이비인후과</label>
                </div>
                <div class="cate2">
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="skin"> 피부과 </label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="hb"> 흉부외과</label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="t"> 치과</label>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="category" value="n"> 내과</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            
            
    
            
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating" id="log2">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="hosAddress1" placeholder="address">
            <label for="floatingInput">지번 주소를 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating" id="log2">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="hosAddress2" placeholder="address">
            <label for="floatingInput">도로명 주소를 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating" id="log2">
            <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="hosNumber" placeholder="number">
            <label for="floatingInput">병원 전화번호를 입력하세요.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkbox mb-3">
            <label>
            <input type="checkbox" value="remember-me" id="flexCheckDefault" > 개인정보 제공 동의
            </label>
        </div>

        <button class="w-30 btn btn-lg btn-dark text-white" type="submit" id="signupBtn"
        onclick="is_checked()">가입하기</button>
        
        <p>* 해당 사이트를 이용하기 위해 병원/약국을 등록하려면 회원가입이 필요합니다.</p>
    
    </div>

